{"tid":313006,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅冠聰遇襲案提堂　20人庭外播紅歌","createTime":"2017-07-08T03:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T13:38:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc8b3903a49080a31cad5e26d3e399c6ec6497a","tid":313006,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:23:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20082761&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20082761%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170708&d=u2iZjVnb%2BmtcLs3ACRVQ46EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=49467f4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20082761%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170708&h=30050708\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20082761&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170708</a><br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰遇襲案提堂　20人庭外播紅歌<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n被告劉必泉（左一）及高傑飛（右一）獲支持者揮舞五星紅旗聲援。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港眾志立法會議員羅冠聰今年1月到台灣，參加當地政黨「時代力量」座談會後回港，在機場遭一群「愛國」滋事者打傷及淋潑液體。5名男女被控非法集結及襲擊羅，其中一名退休漢早前率先提堂，昨在西九龍法院與其餘被告的案件合併處理。兩名無律師代表的退休漢不認罪，其餘被告申請押後答辯。各人繼續保釋待下月18日預審。<br />\n3男2女被告分別是印尼籍送貨工人高傑飛（53歲）、退休漢唐發祥（72歲）和劉必泉（71歲），以及家庭主婦林錦嫦（68歲）和鄺桂嬋（67歲）。他們面對同一項參與非法集結罪；另除劉外，其餘4人各被控一項普通襲擊罪。控罪指各人於今年1月18日犯案。<br />\n<br />\n兩漢否認控罪<br />\n<br />\n無聘用辯護律師的唐及劉否認控罪。其餘3人透過律師指需時索取法律意見。法庭繙譯問明不明白控罪時，劉謂「我冇罪」及「明白，但唔承認」，並稱：「我冇襲擊佢呀！點認罪！」裁判官問有否反對合併案件時，劉搶答「我反對！我單嘢同佢哋冇關係㗎！」另外，20多人到庭聲援揮舞五星紅旗及並播愛國歌。<br />\n案件編號：WKCC3358/17<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪"},{"pid":"b0c619e4490fb771165889f6000032b052ceabef","tid":313006,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170708/large/08la2p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170708%2Flarge%2F08la2p5.jpg&h=ab3fbb7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告劉必泉（左一）及高傑飛（右一）獲支持者揮舞五星紅旗聲援。"},{"pid":"b19a98581687dd62538dd498fc7d0dd34a363449","tid":313006,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:32:25.000Z","msg":"真勇武"},{"pid":"0d9ef41760b662ac7c2140d998d70cf2792c71a8","tid":313006,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f9437c860a57800b0e167a1a2fc3c651b5e4e0","tid":313006,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e34064310b00f2739a8c51b76deecef3920083","tid":313006,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:37:47.000Z","msg":"中間果個好似淨心BB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e85f710598509b3ea3a0d970a84089ccd569945","tid":313006,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:38:13.000Z","msg":"建制派既義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又係俾人導出黎送死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4667ab197ddb451bb683b7324ac29d3bc4d303c4","tid":313006,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:38:45.000Z","msg":"陳淨心又出返嚟?"}]}